## 12. Rule Engine Apply Flow

### Complete Flow Diagram

```
POST /api/engine/apply
         │
         ▼
1. cart.setCurrentDateTime(now)
         │
         ▼
2. validatePromoCodes() [if promoCodes not empty]
   │
   ├── getMaxPromosPerCart()    ← from CACHE (no DB)
   ├── duplicate check
   ├── findByPromoCodeInAndActiveTrue()  ← 1 DB call (batch)
   ├── stackable check (if >1 promo selected)
   ├── findByPromoCodeInAndCustomerId()  ← 1 DB call (batch)
   ├── getTotalUsageByPromoCodeIn()      ← 1 DB call (batch)
   └── validateDateAndUsage() per promo  ← uses pre-fetched maps
         │
         ▼
3. fireRules()
   │
   ├── get KieContainer (AtomicReference, no lock needed for read)
   ├── new DiscountResult() with promoStackLocked=false
   ├── kieSession = container.newKieSession()
   ├── kieSession.insert(cart)
   ├── kieSession.insert(result)
   ├── kieSession.fireAllRules()
   │     │
   │     ├── Rules fire in salience order
   │     ├── Each rule checks: promoStackLocked, isRuleAlreadyFired
   │     ├── Matching rules execute their THEN block
   │     ├── Discounts accumulated in DiscountResult
   │     └── update($result) after each rule
   ├── result.computeFinalTotal()
   └── kieSession.dispose()  ← ALWAYS in finally
         │
         ▼
4. incrementUsage() per applied promo
   │
   └── UPDATE promo_usage + 1 (or INSERT if first use)
         │
         ▼
5. saveAuditLogAsync()  ← @Async — does NOT block response
   │
   └── Save to discount_audit_log in background thread
         │
         ▼
6. Return DiscountResult to client
```

### DiscountResult Object

```
{
  originalTotal:           total before any discounts
  totalDiscount:           sum of all applied discounts
  finalTotal:              originalTotal - totalDiscount (min 0)
  managerApprovalRequired: true if any sys discount needs it
  promoStackLocked:        true if a non-stackable promo applied
  nonStackableLocked:      true if a non-stackable sys discount applied
  firedRuleNames:          Set of rule names that fired (internal)
  appliedDiscounts: [
    {
      ruleName:               identifies which rule
      displayMessage:         customer-facing text
      description:            system discount description
      icon:                   UI icon reference
      discountAmount:         amount discounted
      discountType:           PROMOTION or SYSTEM_DISCOUNT
      stackable:              was this discount stackable
      managerApprovalRequired:needs manager sign-off
    }
  ]
}
```

