### In-Memory Cache

```
WHY: Config is read on EVERY apply request
     DB hit on every request = wasteful (config rarely changes)

HOW:
  ConcurrentHashMap<String, String> configCache
  First request → DB hit → populate cache
  All subsequent requests → cache hit (zero DB)
  Admin updates config → updateConfig() → cache refreshed
  Thread-safe: ConcurrentHashMap handles concurrent reads/writes
```

